### Payment Method Management API Tests
### Requires: Admin authentication
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5056/api
@contentType = application/json

### Get All Payment Methods (Active Only)
GET {{baseUrl}}/payment-methods

### Get All Payment Methods (Including Inactive)
GET {{baseUrl}}/payment-methods?includeInactive=true

### Get Payment Method by ID
@methodId = replace-with-actual-id
GET {{baseUrl}}/payment-methods/{{methodId}}

### Create Custom Payment Method
POST {{baseUrl}}/payment-methods
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "code": "CRYPTO",
  "name": "Criptomonedas",
  "description": "Pago con Bitcoin o Ethereum"
}

### Create Another Payment Method
POST {{baseUrl}}/payment-methods
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

